Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with modal logic and its complexity. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as modal logic is used in AI for reasoning about knowledge and belief. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of modal satisfiability. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) may be relevant as the paper discusses the use of modal circuits. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) may be relevant as modal logic is used in programming language semantics.
